sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Operator
    participant UI as /app/audit
    participant SF as ServerFn
    participant DB as Supabase
    participant W as Worker (external)
    participant P as Playwright

    U->>UI: Click "Run audit"
    UI->>SF: audits.requestAudit({tenantId})
    SF->>DB: insert workflow_runs(state=queued, type=audit)
    SF-->>UI: run_id
    UI->>UI: poll workflow_runs

    W->>DB: claim queued run (state=running)
    W->>P: crawl site (sitemap + sampled pages)
    P-->>W: snapshots + metrics
    W->>W: rule-engine → issues[]
    W->>SF: POST /api/public/worker/audit-callback (HMAC)
    SF->>DB: insert scans + issues + health_scores
    SF->>DB: workflow_runs.state = done
    UI->>SF: poll → done
    UI->>UI: render health score + issues
